lead_paragraph: Loree Moore, a guard for the Liberty, agreed to a three-year contract extension. Moore scored a career-best 9.6 points a game and ranked fourth in the W.N.B.A. with 4.8 assists last season. Her 2.2 steals a game ranked second in the league.
